</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_151" id="75r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Wilhelm Hasen von Waldeck</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als vor <expan>czeite<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        der hochgeporn fürst und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> Jost von Merhern
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>kauffleut<ex>en</ex></expan> ir
                        habe und <expan>kauffmansch<ex>aft</ex></expan> czu Prunne
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, darümb wir im nü newlich
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wol czu wissen getan, wie ir in
                                <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> gen
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joste<ex>n</ex></expan> vast fürderlich und beholffen
                                <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> seit, des wir euch mit
                                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                            <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>; und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell <expan>fleiszikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir fürbaz den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darynne <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Laur<ex>encii</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Den edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Laczko von Krabarn
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>;
                                <lb/><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> Örtell,
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu Prag,
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
